107
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:13,251
Sophocles wrote the oracle
so that it was unconditional,

108
00:15:13,314 --> 00:15:17,276
meaning, Heracles never had
any choice, right?

109
00:15:17,345 --> 00:15:20,169
