Um, about which part?

115
00:15:37,022 --> 00:15:38,111
I think it's more tragic

116
00:15:38,113 --> 00:15:39,887
because if it's all
just inevitable,

117
00:15:39,889 --> 00:15:42,306
then that means that
the characters had no hope.

118
00:15:42,414 --> 00:15:43,215
They never had hope

119
00:15:43,217 --> 00:15:45,103
because they're all just,
like, hopeless.

120
00:15:45,201 --> 00:15:46,062
