00:20:00,305 --> 00:20:01,546
Maybe not.

154
00:20:02,010 --> 00:20:04,828
Okay. No pressure.

155
00:20:12,475 --> 00:20:13,608
My name's Annie.

156
00:20:13,834 --> 00:20:15,139
Hi, Annie.

157
00:20:16,819 --> 00:20:18,676
My mom died a week ago.

158
00:20:18,967 --> 00:20:22,153
So I'm just here
for trying it.

159
00:20:23,211 --> 00:20:25,745
I have a lot of resistance
to things like this,

160
00:20:25,863 --> 00:20:28,901
but I came to these
a couple years ago.

161
00:20:28,942 --> 00:20:32,049
Well, I was forced to come
and I guess it, um...

162
00:20:33,466 --> 00:20:35,435
I guess it helped. So, um...

163
00:20:38,422 --> 00:20:42,014
My mom was old and she wasn't
all together there at the end.

164
00:20:42,095 --> 00:20:44,439
And we were pretty much
estranged before that,

165
00:20:44,441 --> 00:20:47,362
so it really wasn't
a huge blow.

166
00:20:47,654 --> 00:20:52,894
But I did love her.

167
00:20:54,325 --> 00:20:55,774
And she didn't have
an easy life.

168
00:20:55,825 --> 00:20:58,961
She had DID, which became
extreme at the end.

169
00:20:59,180 --> 00:21:00,645
And dementia.

170
00:21:00,747 --> 00:21:04,781
And my father died when I was
a baby from starvation,

171
00:21:04,862 --> 00:21:07,679
um, because he had
psychotic depression

172
00:21:07,749 --> 00:21:08,476
and he starved himself,

173
00:21:08,478 --> 00:21:10,744
which I'm sure was just
as pleasant as it sounds.

174
00:21:10,801 --> 00:21:12,333
And then there's my brother.

175
00:21:12,483 --> 00:21:14,383
My older brother
had schizophrenia

176
00:21:14,447 --> 00:21:15,713
and when he was 16

177
00:21:15,752 --> 00:21:17,488
