And then we were.

186
00:21:52,129 --> 00:21:53,684
She's completely manipulative.

187
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:57,105
Until my husband finally
enforced a no-contact rule,

188
00:21:57,163 --> 00:21:59,426
which lasted until I got
pregnant with my daughter.

189
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:00,591
I didn't let her
anywhere near me

190
00:22:00,593 --> 00:22:02,245
when I had my first, my son,

191
00:22:02,298 --> 00:22:04,112
which is why I gave her
my daughter,

192
00:22:04,114 --> 00:22:06,576
who she immediately
stabbed her hooks into.

193
00:22:06,951 --> 00:22:09,668
And I just...
I felt guilty again.

194
00:22:09,711 --> 00:22:11,149
I felt guilty again.

195
00:22:11,405 --> 00:22:12,447
When she got sick,

196
00:22:12,449 --> 00:22:14,688
not that she was really even
my mom at the end,

197
00:22:14,690 --> 00:22:19,324
and not that she would ever
feel guilty about anything.

198
00:22:23,926 --> 00:22:27,473
