any more stress on my family.

199
00:22:29,780 --> 00:22:32,102
I'm not even really sure
if they could...

200
00:22:33,679 --> 00:22:35,512
Could give me that support.

201
00:22:39,005 --> 00:22:40,839
And I just...
I just feel like...

202
00:22:44,341 --> 00:22:46,397
I just sometimes
feel like it's all ruined.

203
00:22:49,194 --> 00:22:53,362
And then I realize
that I am to blame.

204
00:22:55,970 --> 00:22:57,003
Or not that I'm to blame,

205
00:22:57,048 --> 00:23:01,816
but I am blamed! I'm...

